E%3Cli%3EClient-facing%20roles%20are%20growing%20by%2025%25%2C%20while%20non-client-facing%20roles%20are%20shrinking.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMcKinsey%20now%20employs%2040%2C000%20people%20and%2025%2C000%20AI%20agents%2C%20and%20could%20have%20equal%20numbers%20by%20year-end.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmbb-leaders-consulting-firms-advising-leaders-and-ceos-2025-7%23%3A~%3Atext%3DYou%2520might%2520not%2520know%2520their%2CMcKinsey%252C%2520Bain%252C%2520and%2520BCG.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMcKinsey's%20top%20executive%3C%2Fa%3E%20shared%20some%20hard%20numbers%20on%20how%20AI%20is%20reshaping%20the%20consulting%20giant's%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-head-bob-sternfels-leadership-tips-focus-ai-employee-development-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBob%20Sternfels%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20McKinsey's%20global%20managing%20partner%2C%20appeared%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fannouncements-coming-out-of-ces-nvidia-vera-rubin-autonmous-vehicle-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EConsumer%20Electronics%20Show%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20a%20live%20taping%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BAll-In%26quot%3B%20podcast%20with%20co-host%20Jason%20Calacanis%20and%20Hemant%20Taneja%2C%20CEO%20of%20General%20Catalyst.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESternfels%20said%20AI%20has%20fundamentally%20changed%20how%20McKinsey%20staffs%20its%20business%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20add%20and%20cut%20jobs%20in%20equal%20measure%20while%20still%20achieving%20overall%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20it%20as%20the%20%26quot%3B25%20squared%26quot%3B%20approach%2C%20Sternfels%20said%20McKinsey%20is%20growing%20its%20client-facing%20roles%20%E2%80%94%20what%20you%20typically%20picture%20when%20you%20think%20of%20a%20McKinsey%20consultant%20%E2%80%94%20by%2025%25.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20said%20non-client-facing%20roles%2C%20which%20make%20up%20the%20other%20half%20of%20its%20workforce%2C%20have%20shrunk%20by%20about%2025%25%20while%20output%20from%20that%20side%20has%20grown%2010%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20model%20has%20always%20been%20synonymous%20that%20growth%20only%20occurs%20with%20total%20head%20count%20growth.%20Now%20it's%20actually%20splitting.%20We%20can%20grow%20in%20this%20part%2C%20the%20client-facing%20side%2C%20and%20we%20can%20shrink%20in%20this%20part%20and%20have%20aggregate%20growth%20in%20total%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20new%20paradigm%20and%20a%20new%20dynamic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESternfels%20said%20the%20firm%20has%20seen%20massive%20productivity%20gains%20as%20it's%20embraced%20AI%2C%20saving%201.5%20million%20hours%20in%20search%20and%20synthesis%20work%20last%20year%20alone.%20Instead%20of%20doing%20the%20work%20that's%20typically%20done%20by%20more%20junior%20employees%2C%20he%20said%20McKinsey%20consultants%20are%20%26quot%3Bmoving%20up%20the%20stack%26quot%3B%20and%20tackling%20more%20complicated%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcKinsey%20employees%20also%20have%20a%20brand%20new%20set%20of%20coworkers%20that%20are%20increasingly%20becoming%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20the%20company%3A%20AI%20agents%2C%20which%20can%20act%20independently%20like%20digital%20employees.%20Sternfels%20said%20that%20as%20of%20last%20week%2C%20the%20company%20had%2040%2C000%20human%20employees%20and%2025%2C000%20personalized%20agents.%20Sternfels%20said%20AI%20agents%20are%20able%20to%20handle%20entire%20job%20functions%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20expects%20McKinsey%20to%20have%20about%20the%20same%20number%20of%20AI%20agents%20as%20human%20employees%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20young%20professionals%20coming%20into%20the%20workforce%2C%20Sternfels%20said%20they%20should%20think%20about%20honing%20skills%20that%20AI%20can't%20do%2C%20setting%20the%20right%20aspirations%2C%20human%20judgment%2C