gcaption%3EToday%2C%20recruiting%20numbers%20are%20on%20the%20upswing%20for%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20boosted%20in%20part%20by%20%26quot%3Bpre-boot%20camp%26quot%3B%20preparatory%20courses%20created%20by%20the%20Army%20and%20the%20Navy%20for%20help%20filling%20their%20ranks.%20The%20Marine%20Corps%2C%20the%20smallest%20branch%20of%20the%20military%20besides%20the%20Space%20Force%2C%20does%20not%20offer%20such%20a%20course.%3Cp%3EDefense%20Visual%20Information%20Distribution%20Service%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20longtime%20recruiting%20official%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20officer%20reliefs%20slowed%20after%20then-Major%20Gen.%20William%20Bowers%20took%20command%20in%202022%20and%20oversaw%20an%20external%20study%20on%20shifting%20demographics%20of%20potential%20recruits.%20Such%20surveys%20are%20designed%20to%20give%20recruiting%20leaders%20an%20early%20read%20on%20population%20shifts%20and%20how%20willingness%20to%20serve%20varies%20across%20different%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pandemic%20%26quot%3Bplaced%20a%20level%20of%20strain%20on%20the%20recruiting%20enterprise%20that%20was%20unlike%20anything%20we've%20experienced%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Marine%20Corps%20Recruiting%20Command%20spokesman%20acknowledged%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20Recruiters%2C%20and%20those%20in%20charge%20of%20them%2C%20were%20up%20against%20%26quot%3Bextraordinary%20pressure%26quot%3B%20and%20facing%20%26quot%3Bextreme%20conditions%20felt%20across%20the%20entire%20recruiting%20enterprise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecruiting%20across%20the%20military%20has%20recently%20been%20on%20the%20uptick.%20New%20Pentagon%20figures%20show%20a%20strong%20start%20to%20fiscal%20year%202026%2C%20boosted%20by%20Army%20and%20Navy%20pre-boot%20camp%20preparatory%20courses%20that%20help%20low-scoring%20or%20overweight%20applicants%20increase%20scores%20and%20fitness%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpentagon-ig-report-arm