20says%20China%20is%20going%20to%20%26quot%3Bhave%20more%20power%20than%20anyone%20else%20and%20probably%20will%20have%20more%20chips.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EEvelyn%20Hockstein%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElon%20Musk%20says%20China%20is%20poised%20to%20lead%20the%20world%20in%20AI%20compute.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChina's%20electricity%20advantage%20could%20give%20it%20an%20edge%20in%20scaling%20AI%20systems.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChina%20will%20also%20%26quot%3Bfigure%20out%20the%20chips%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20China%20is%20on%20track%20to%20outpace%20every%20other%20country%20in%20the%20computing%20power%20needed%20to%20run%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%20CEO%20said%20in%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BMoonshots%20with%20Peter%20Diamandis%26quot%3B%20podcast%20published%20Tuesday%20that%20%26quot%3BChina's%20going%20to%20have%20more%20power%20than%20anyone%20else%20and%20probably%20will%20have%20more%20chips.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20current%20trends%2C%20China%20will%20far%20exceed%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20in%20AI%20compute%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20China's%20decisive%20advantage%20in%20the%20AI%20race%20lies%20in%20its%20ability%20to%20scale%20electricity%20generation.%20He%20estimated%20that%20China%20could%20reach%20about%20three%20times%20the%20electricity%20output%20of%20the%20US%20by%202026%2C%20giving%20it%20the%20capacity%20to%20support%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-center-development-true-cost-environmental-impact-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eenergy-hungry%20AI%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElectricity%20generation%20is%20the%20limiting%20factor%20to%20scaling%20AI%20systems%2C%20Musk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20underestimating%20the%20difficulty%20of%20bringing%20electricity%20online%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20US%20has%20focused%20on%20restricting%20China's%20access%20to%20advanced%20semiconductors%2C%20Musk%20suggested%20those%20constraints%20may%20matter%20less%20over%20time.%20China%20will%20%26quot%3Bfigure%20out%20the%20chips%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20added%20that%20diminishing%20returns%20at%20the%20cutting%20edge%20of%20chip%20performance%20might%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20China%20to%20catch%20up%2C%20even%20without%20access%20to%20the%20most%20advanced%20designs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20previously%20pointed%20to%20China%20as%20a%20model%20in%20areas%20beyond%20AI%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BPeople%20by%20WTF%26quot%3B%20podcast%20published%20in%20November%2C%20Musk%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20turn%20his%20social%20media%20platform%20X%20into%20%26quot%3BWeChat%2B%2B%2C%26quot%3B%20referencing%20China's%20dominant%20super%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20also%20like%20the%20idea%20of%20sort%20of%20having%20a%20unified%20app%20or%20website%20or%20whatever%2C%20where%20you%20can%20do%20anything%20you%20want%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BChina%20has%20this%20with%20WeChat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220400a178-d53b-41d5-a836-79d5ff955179%5C%22%3EAI's%20next%20bottleneck%20is%20power%20%E2%80%94%20and%20China%20is%20leading%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20comments%20come%20as%20energy%20supply%20and%20data%20infrastructure%20emerge%20as%20key%20constraints%20in%20scaling%20AI%2C%20rather%20than%20chips%20or%20algorithms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20worldwide%20have%20rushed%20to%20build%20AI%20data%20centers%2C%20many%20of%20which%20require%20as%20much%20electrical%20power%20as%20small%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-centers-us-chips-electricit