a%20community%20of%20people%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewho%20are%20trained%20in%20keeping%20an%20eye%20out%20for%20elephant%20movements.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20in%20Kaziranga%2C%20there%20are%20groups%20of%20young%20boys%20who%20are%20on%20alert.%20They%20stop%20cars%20to%20allow%20the%20elephants%20to%20cross.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fourth%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20is%20to%20relocate%20villages.%20This%20%E2%80%9Clast-ditch%20effort%E2%80%9D%20is%20only%20resorted%20to%20in%20areas%20where%20people%20have%20settled%20right%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20elephant%20corridors%20and%20elephants%20are%20killing%20them%20and%20not%20letting%20crops%20grow%2C%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-500x672.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vivek%20Menon%20and%20elephants%20share%20a%20bond%20of%20love%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-500x672.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-223x300.jpg%20223w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-768x1033.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-1142x1536.jpg%201142w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-1523x2048.jpg%201523w%2C%20https%3A%2